Global 3D Printed Gas Turbine Market Insights
3D Printed Gas Turbine Market size was valued at USD 0.47 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.68 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 24.5% from 2024 to 2030.

3D Printed Gas Turbine Market Overview
The 3D printed gas turbine market is experiencing significant growth, driven by advancements in additive manufacturing technologies and the increasing demand for efficient, lightweight components in the aerospace and energy sectors. The integration of 3D printing allows for the production of complex turbine parts with reduced lead times and enhanced performance characteristics. This trend is expected to continue, with the market projected to reach substantial valuations in the coming years. Source

